quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  6,111,"N’iyo tuza kubamanurira abamalayika, (tukabazurira) abapfuye bakabavugisha, tukanabateranyiriza buri kintu imbona nkubone (nk’uko babyifuzaga), ntibari kwemera keretse Allah abishatse. Ariko abenshi muri bo bafite ubujiji"
  6,112,"Uko ni na ko buri muhanuzi twamushyiriyeho abanzi, (abo banzi ni) amashitani (aboneka) mu bantu n’amajini. Bamwe muri bo bahishurira abandiimvugo zitatse ikinyoma zigamije kubashuka. N’iyo Nyagasani wawe aza kubishaka ntibari kubikora; bityo bareke n’ibyo bihimbira"
  6,113,"(Ibi) ni no kugira ngo imitima ya babandi batemera imperuka izibogamireho (izo mvugo z’ibishuko) izishimire, no kugira ngo bakore ibyo bakora (ibyaha by’ingeri zose)"
  6,114,"Ese utari Allah ni we nagira umukiranuzi kandi ari we (Allah) wabahishuriye igitabo gisobanutse? Kandi babanditwahaye ibitabo (Tawurati n’Ivanjili) bazi ko cyahishuwe (igitabo cya Qur’an) giturutse kwaNyagasani wawe mu kuri. Ku bw’ibyo, uramenye ntuzabe mu bashidikanya"
  6,115,"N’ijambo rya Nyagasani wawe ryarasohoye mu kuri no mu butabera. Ntawahindura amagambo ye. Ni na weUwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  6,116,"Kandi nuramuka wumviye abenshi mu bari ku isi, bazakuyobya inzira ya Allah. Nta kindibakurikira kitari ugukeka,ndetse nta n’icyo bakora kitari ukubeshya"
  6,117,"Mu by’ ukuri, Nyagasani wawe ni we uzi neza abayobye inzira ye, kandi ni we uzi neza abayobotse"
  6,118,"Bityo, nimuryeibyavugiweho izina rya Allah (bibagwa), niba muri abemera amagambo ye (Qur’an)"